### SocialGraph API Endpoints

### Status endpoint (no authentication required)
GET https://localhost/api/v1/socialgraph/status
Accept: application/json

### Get connections for authenticated user
GET https://localhost/api/v1/socialgraph/connections
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Get connections for a specific user
GET https://localhost/api/v1/socialgraph/connections/123
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Follow a user
POST https://localhost/api/v1/socialgraph/follow/123
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Unfollow a user
DELETE https://localhost/api/v1/socialgraph/follow/123
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

